Class FlatType

java.lang.Object
sg.edu.ntu.sc2002.ay2425.fcsdGroup2.model.entities.FlatType
public class FlatType extends Object
Represents a type of flat in a BTO project. Contains details like size, total units, selling price, and target applicant groups.
